&quot;USE &#039;EM OR LOSE &#039;EM: All Promo Helper bonuses will be reset at the beginning of the 2016 ranked season&quot; 

Does whatever rank you gain during the preseason pointless because it will reset during the start of the official season?

Example: I am Silver4 and want to try to get to Gold as soon as possible. If I get Gold during the preseason, will the reset & send me back to Silver4? Or will placements place me around what I ended up with at the very end of preseason?
